<!--ABOUT MODAL-->
<div class="modal modal-dialog-scrollable fade" id="about" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel"
     aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content bg-dark text-white">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">About</h5>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <p>with this app, you can browse a NASA APOD (astronomy picture of the day)
                    service and image viewer from space.
                    <br>to get started, follow the steps:
                </p>

                <ol>
                    <li>First select a date from the calendar, so you
                        can see photos or videos from the selected day till today
                    </li>
                    <li>Click the search button and the photos/videos will be shown</li>
                    <li>You can click the 'description' button to see the description of the selected photos
                    </li>
                    <li>You can click the 'comments' button to see others comments of this photo</li>
                    <li>Simply enter your comment in the text field then click the "pos" button to share it</li>
                    <li>Your comment will be added to the comments section, and you can simply delete it</li>
                    <li>You can click on the image to see it on full screen if it is a
                        video you can click on 'full screen' button
                    </li>
                </ol>

                <p>Thank you for using our app ðŸ¤­</p>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>